| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3618 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 537bbbbc-9019-5592-8360-26c1de1ff0e9"
